The network of interest it the one showed in Fig. 1. Details about the network construction are reported in Subheadings 2.1 and 3.1. For each species in the network, i.e., each mRNA (capital letters) and correspondent protein concentration (small letters), we wrote one equation, which expresses its change in time as the result of production and degradation:
